                  Known Water Taxi Operators (Taxi-Marítimo)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-3 leading-relaxed">The following operators appear regularly in pilgrim community reports on Gronze.com, the Camino de Santiago forums, and the Confraternity of Saint James bulletin. These are local fishermen running informal river crossings — their availability is seasonal and subject to river conditions. <strong class="text-slate-300">Contact numbers change; always verify through your accommodation or the tourist office the night before.</strong></p>
