                    Departure — Portugal
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Cais da Rua dos Pescadores</strong>, Caminha. The fishermen's dock is located immediately adjacent to the main ferry berth on the northern waterfront. Look for the traditional wooden fishing boats moored below the embankment wall.</p>
